dct_title_s: World deepwater : oil and gas activity and concession map 2013. (title panel)
dct_description_sm: Shows gas fields, oil fields, gas pipelines, oil pipelines, refineries, concession blocks. Includes 29 insets maps, location map, statistical tables, and color advertisements. Includes graphs and charts showing timescale and production statistics. Includes legend.
